^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Okay, this was really a fairly straight forward hand had spades broken. In IMPs, Kia's line of play is fine but you can make 5. Starting to draw trump was fine. But once they break 4-1 you should abandon trump and play a heart. Then you can ruff dummy's last heart in your hand, and only lose 1 spade and 1 heart. If Elizabeth draws your last two trumps, you can pitch dummy's third heart on your K of clubs. Alternatively, you can unblock the Ace of clubs at trick two and then after drawing trumps, pitch dummy's last heart on the King of clubs.|
