^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Anna asked if I would bid 1S or 2S with her hand.  I would overcall 1S, as I think she is too strong for 2S. But 2S could work out, and it turns out it works better on this hand. It gives me a big problem. I like my heart support and singleton spade but am a bit weak for 3H. I probably bid 3H anyway, and Kia bids 4.|
